               <history>
                  <origin notBefore="1635" notAfter="1645">
                     <p>
                        <list>
                           <item>Handritið var skrifað á <origPlace key="IS">Íslandi</origPlace>
                              <origDate notBefore="1635" notAfter="1646">fyrir 1646</origDate> (sbr.
                                 <locus from="accMat01r" to="accMat01r">seðil</locus>). Það er
                              tímasett til fyrri hluta 17. aldar í <bibl>
                                 <ref target="KKKat">Katalog I</ref>
                              </bibl>, bls. 137. </item>
                           <item>Það var upprunalega hluti af stærri bók sem innihélt einnig <ref target="AM02-0011" type="ms">AM 11 fol.</ref>, <ref target="AM02-0050a" type="ms">AM 50 a fol.</ref>, <ref target="AM02-0151" type="ms">AM 151 fol.</ref>, <ref target="AM02-0164a" type="ms">AM 164 a fol.</ref>, <ref target="AM02-0165a" type="ms">AM 165 a fol.</ref>, <ref target="AM02-0165b" type="ms">AM 165 b fol.</ref>, <ref target="AM02-0165d" type="ms">AM 165 d fol.</ref>, <ref target="AM02-0165e" type="ms">AM 165 e fol.</ref>, <ref target="AM02-0165g" type="ms">AM 165 g fol.</ref>, <ref target="AM02-0165h" type="ms">AM 165 h fol.</ref>, <ref target="AM02-0165i" type="ms">AM 165 i fol.</ref>, <ref target="AM02-0165k" type="ms">AM 165 k fol.</ref>, <ref target="AM02-0165l" type="ms">AM 165 l fol.</ref>, <ref target="AM02-0165m" type="ms">AM 165 m fol.</ref>, <ref target="AM02-0202a" type="ms">AM 202 a fol.</ref>, <ref target="AM02-0202g" type="ms">AM 202 g fol.</ref>, <ref target="AM02-0202i" type="ms">AM 202 i fol.</ref>
